Package: CrossVA
Type: Package
Title: Verbal Autopsy Data Transform for Use with Various Coding Algorithms
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R: person("Nicolas", "Maire", email = "nicolas.maire@unibas.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Enables transformation of Verbal Autopsy data collected with the WHO 2016 questionnaire
  for automated coding of Cause of Death using different computer algorithms. Currently supports user-supplied mappings,
  and provides unvalidated mapping definitions to transform to InterVA4, Tariff 2, and InSilicoVA.
  This package is made available by WHO, in collaboration with Swiss Tropical and Public Health Institute.
License: GPL-2
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Imports: lubridate
